OutText.#text:
Our travel rewards card will really take you places! You'll earn 3 Neptune Airlines miles for every $1 you spend on Neptune Airlines, 2 miles for every $1 spent at restaurants, gas stations, department stores, grocery stores, and on Neomart.com, plus 1 mile per dollar on all other purchases. We'll also give you a one-time welcome bonus of 75,000 miles if you spend $2000 in the first 3 months. Would you like to apply now or do you have more questions about this card?
